Master

Class Master.CSInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • Master.Master.CSInfo
  • Enclosing class:
    Master

    private class Master.CSInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class CSInfo is used by master to maintain metadata for connecting to various chunkservers. It keeps track of the most recent heartbeat time received from the chunkserver, the status of the chunkserver, and the chunkserver ID.
    Author:
    lazzarid
